    "In ScienceQA, human performance reaches up to 90.23% accuracy, while the random performance is only 40.28%.",
    "Among many of the systems evaluated, the MiniGPT-4 model trained in a zero-shot setting only achieves 43.83% accuracy (Zheng et al., 2023), a slight improvement over random performance, which denotes the inherent difficulty of the benchmark.",
